<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Campaign Goal Reached!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd89b 0%, #19547b 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .celebration-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .achievement-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd89b 0%, #19547b 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .achievement-box .goal-amount {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .achievement-box .label {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .stat-card .number {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #19547b;
    }
    .stat-card .label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
    .next-steps {
      background-color: #e7f3ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #19547b;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="celebration-icon">ðŸŽ‰</div>
      <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px;">Your Campaign Reached Its Goal!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{organizerName}},</p>
      <p><strong>Amazing news!</strong> Your campaign has successfully reached its fundraising goal!</p>

      <div class="achievement-box">
        <div class="label">Goal Achieved</div>
        <div class="goal-amount">{{currency}} {{goalAmount}}</div>
        <div>{{campaignTitle}}</div>
      </div>

      <h3>Campaign Impact</h3>
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="number">{{totalDonors}}</div>
          <div class="label">Total Donors</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="number">{{currency}} {{goalAmount}}</div>
          <div class="label">Funds Raised</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>This incredible achievement wouldn't have been possible without:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Your dedication</strong> in creating and managing this campaign</li>
        <li><strong>The generosity</strong> of {{totalDonors}} donors who believed in your cause</li>
        <li><strong>The power of community</strong> coming together for positive change</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #19547b;">What's Next?</h3>
        <ul style="margin-bottom: 0;">
          <li>Review your campaign dashboard to see donor details</li>
          <li>Consider sending a thank you message to your supporters</li>
          <li>Plan how you'll use the funds to maximize impact</li>
          <li>Keep your donors updated on the progress and outcomes</li>
          <li>Share success stories to inspire others</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>Thank you for using our platform to make a difference. Your success story will inspire others to take action!</p>
      <p><strong>Keep changing the world!</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 CareForAll. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>You're making a difference in the community!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
